  "reference_number": "RUS1657",
  "remarks": "\nAirat Mintimerovich Shaimiev (hereafter SHAIMIEV) is an involved person under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 on the basis of the following grounds: \n(1) SHAIMIEV is and has been involved in obtaining a benefit from or supporting the Government of Russia by working as a director or equivalent of OAO Tatavtodor, a Government of Russia-affiliated entity which is carrying on business in sectors of strategic significance to the Government of Russia, namely the Russian construction and transport sectors. \n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
